## 2) Scripts Capability

**Purpose:** repeatable verification, drift detection, doc enforcement, and (for orchestrator-pattern repos) session-brief sync. **This is the section most often skipped during retrofits.**

**You should have** (copy any that match your project's needs):

| Script | Purpose | Copy from |
|---|---|---|
| `scripts/verify.sh` | The repo's canonical verify gate (handoff signal) | (project-specific; create if missing) |
| `scripts/check_template_drift.sh` | Detects drift between applied templates and the source pack | `templates-v2/scripts/check_template_drift.sh.template` |
| `scripts/enforce_doc_updates.sh` | Fails CI when behavior changed without doc updates | `templates-v2/scripts/enforce_doc_updates.sh.template` |
| `scripts/predeploy_full_suite.sh` | Composite pre-deploy gate | `templates-v2/scripts/predeploy_full_suite.sh.template` |
| `scripts/validate_context_budget.sh` | Keeps the AI startup context under budget | `templates-v2/scripts/validate_context_budget.sh.template` |
| `scripts/validate_templates.sh` | Validates placeholders, presence, drift in one call | `templates-v2/scripts/validate_templates.sh.template` |
| `scripts/sync_session_brief.sh` | Regenerates `docs/SESSION_BRIEF.md` (lean profile only) | `templates-v2/scripts/sync_session_brief.sh.template` |
| `scripts/bump_version.sh` | Single-source-of-truth version bump (if project has versions) | (project-specific; if it exists in the project, register it as a trigger below) |

**Triggers to register in `docs/CONTEXT_ROUTING.md` § Event Triggers:**
- "About to bump or compare versions" → `scripts/bump_version.sh` (fail loudly if missing — see §6)
- "About to merge to main" → `scripts/predeploy_full_suite.sh`
- "Behavior change without doc update suspected" → `scripts/enforce_doc_updates.sh`
- "Template version bump" → `scripts/check_template_drift.sh` and `docs/UPGRADE_GUIDE.md`

**Proves it works:** `ls scripts/ && bash scripts/verify.sh`
- [ ] All applicable scripts present and executable (`chmod +x scripts/*.sh`), triggers registered, or N/A:

