- `docs/APPLY_CHECKLIST.md` — worker pre-return ritual (do not confuse with the *template* `APPLY_CHECKLIST.md`)
- `docs/POST_CODING_CHECKS.md` — mandatory cloud-orchestrator review of every DONE packet
- `docs/INVESTIGATOR_PROTOCOL.md` — escalation role
- `AI_AGENT.md` § Orchestrator Rails populated (10 hard rules, decision tree, unattended run rules)

**Copy from:** the asus repo (`/home/mamana/private-repos/asus/docs/`) is the reference implementation; or a known-good orchestrator-pattern project.

**Triggers to register in `docs/CONTEXT_ROUTING.md` § Event Triggers:**
- "Issuing a worker packet" → `docs/WORKER_TASK_PACKET.md`
- "Worker returned DONE" → `docs/POST_CODING_CHECKS.md` (mandatory review)
- "Worker returned BLOCKED twice on same Path ID" → `docs/INVESTIGATOR_PROTOCOL.md`
- "About to run unattended overnight" → `AI_AGENT.md` § Unattended Run Rules

**Proves it works:** dry-run a packet end-to-end on a trivial change.
