## 8) Final Adoption Gate

Run in order; all must pass:

1. `bash scripts/verify.sh` (or project verify gate) — exit 0
2. `bash scripts/check_template_drift.sh . path/to/templates-v2` — exit 0
3. `scripts/validate_templates.sh` (if present) — exit 0
4. Complete `docs/TEMPLATE_VALIDATION_CHECKLIST.md` — every box checked
5. Push a no-op commit; confirm CI green
6. Update `CHANGELOG.md` `Unreleased`: "Adopted templates-v2 vN.N via TEMPLATE_ADOPTION_WALKTHROUGH; sections completed: ..."

- [ ] All six pass.

Adoption is complete when this box is checked. Until then, the AI should treat the project as *partially adopted* and surface unchecked sections at the start of every session.
